    "True hybrid, combining one-stage (initial proposals) and two-stage (refinement).",
    "Yes Multi-stage learning with SGD: Smooth L1 loss for bounding box regression, softmax loss for classification Cai and Nuno, 2018 Mask R-CNN with Cascaded Head Kailin He, Georgia Gkioxari, Piotr Dollar, Ross Girshick (2017) Two-stage: Uses standard Mask R-CNN for region proposals (no cascade for proposals).",
